{"tid":1537501,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"到左今時今日，係咪應該要轉下型抗爭？","createTime":"2019-09-04T02:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T05:10:42.000Z","uid":98068,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0e5bbde00b99d86ea3ba46abb7a2a02e49beb7e1","tid":1537501,"uid":98068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:53:51.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲用固有示威思考方式真係唔夠<br />\n香港要嘅係抗爭，唔係示威<br />\n<br />\n我地唯一嘅優勢係人多<br />\n當警狗燒煙，再衝出黎捉人<br />\n我好明白大家當下係會驚，想走<br />\n<br />\n但轉個方向諗，我地人多，同佢地打係咪真係冇得打？<br />\n可能根本對面見我地唔走，佢地唔敢衝入黎<br />\n要打，我地十個打佢地一個，未必會輸<br />\n但每次少啲，每次少啲<br />\n到最後得番一個打一個，我地就冇得番身<br />\n<br />\n我唔想再見到有兄弟比狗打死，比狗拗斷手，打到入廠<br />\n要拉，我地幾萬人一齊係拘留中心抗爭<br />\n我地係兄弟，係手足，唔可以再掉低任何一個"},{"pid":"b416c4f23bc978415b764ba1b525138599bfb4d9","tid":1537501,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:54:13.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a85354b686eac39e7726d1c40cbe7e54cac76c0","tid":1537501,"uid":267425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:54:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n唔該入去幫p牌仔推一推 好人一世平安<br />\n<br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fLDFcUN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLDFcUN.jpg&h=350c6ca1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d39c5885e33047c580020c143b11325f9c67bdeb","tid":1537501,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQ0Tyrc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQ0Tyrc.jpg&h=d900eccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a>"},{"pid":"f368d362189879e7afcaf9cb02e575f87146d375","tid":1537501,"uid":29276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:56:04.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"d59dc4e5f6ad709d22fa056ee9308ebce639cd51","tid":1537501,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHcuNJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHcuNJL.jpg&h=417a49e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不反對通知書申請中<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9月6日 反濫捕 抗威權集會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535223</a>"},{"pid":"91b21225297c8b69020eb27d3e09b51c7b54718d","tid":1537501,"uid":98068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:13:10.000Z","msg":"自推，搶埋d狗嘅gear，要佢跪係前線"},{"pid":"e04feec1d3cc4520b2ef6266c5f463a8d31435f2","tid":1537501,"uid":98068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:42:23.000Z","msg":"一推再推"},{"pid":"1d9e24cb981c8d40af4f6d9522b2c5ea1fea1e24","tid":1537501,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b4e9f8c474587d21da08ad00c20b6cbdb69dcb3","tid":1537501,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e5bbde00b99d86ea3ba46abb7a2a02e49beb7e1","tid":1537501,"uid":98068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:53:51.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲用固有示威思考方式真係唔夠<br />\n香港要嘅係抗爭，唔係示威<br />\n<br />\n我地唯一嘅優勢係人多<br />\n當警狗燒煙，再衝出黎捉人<br />\n我好明白大家當下係會驚，想走<br />\n<br />\n但轉個方向諗，我地人多，同佢地打係咪真係冇得打？<br />\n可能根本對面見我地唔走，佢地唔敢衝入黎<br />\n要打，我地十個打佢地一個，未必會輸<br />\n但每次少啲，每次少啲<br />\n到最後得番一個打一個，我地就冇得番身<br />\n<br />\n我唔想再見到有兄弟比狗打死，比狗拗斷手，打到入廠<br />\n要拉，我地幾萬人一齊係拘留中心抗爭<br />\n我地係兄弟，係手足，唔可以再掉低任何一個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:43:04.000Z","msg":"問題係個社會仲有好多人有負擔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cl